We need to prove two lemmas:
1. `locally_rightContinuous_iff`: This lemma states that `Locally (fun X ↦ ∀ ω, Function.RightContinuous (X · ω)) 𝓕 X P` is equivalent to `∀ᵐ ω ∂P, Function.RightContinuous (X · ω)`.
